CHAT: Global in-character chat channel

Syntax: chat <message>
        chat off
        chat on

Global in-character chat channel. Reaches all online players who have
chat enabled. Distinct from OOC, which is for out-of-character talk.

  chat <message>    broadcast on the chat channel
  chat off          stop receiving chat messages
  chat on           resume receiving chat messages

SEE ALSO: ooc, say, radio, shout
